# Cieden Assistant Development Rules

## Project Context
- Cieden AI Sales & Consulting Assistant (UI/UX design and software development company)
- Voice and text powered with ElevenLabs
- Visual AI with CopilotKit
- Real-time with Convex
- No bank/financial assistant persona — agent represents Cieden only

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15.4 with App Router
- TypeScript (strict mode)
- Convex for backend
- CopilotKit self-hosted runtime
- ElevenLabs ConvAI CLI
- Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui

## Code Standards
- Feature-based folder structure
- Self-hosted CopilotKit for low latency
- Convex for all state management
- Mobile-first responsive design
- Performance target: <500ms voice-to-chart

## Key Patterns
- No zustand (Convex handles state)
- Direct OpenAI integration (not cloud)
- Hybrid ElevenLabs widget approach
- Edge functions for webhooks